OL,5,G1100 The Tall Men
OL,6,     F(1955) Western. Clark Gable plays
OL,7,     Fa Civil War veteran who, with his
OL,8,     Fbrother (Cameron Mitchell),
OL,9,     Faccepts the role of trail boss on
OL,10,     Fa huge cattle drive for a crooked
OL,11,     Fcattleman (Robert Ryan).
OL,12,G1325 They Rode West
OL,13,     F(1954) Tough western. A cavalry
OL,14,     Fdoctor (Robert Francis) discovers
OL,15,     Fa Native American tribe is dying
OL,16,     Fof malaria, but his by-the-book
OL,17,     Fcaptain (Phil Carey) refuses to
OL,18,     Fallow their treatment.
