OL,5,G1505 The Sheriff of Fractured Jaw
OL,6,     F(1959) Comedy western with Kenneth
OL,7,     FMore. An English gunsmith decides
OL,8,     Fthe Wild West is the best market
OL,9,     Ffor his wares, but little does he
OL,10,     Fexpect to end up sheriff of a
OL,11,     Flawless frontier town.
